thread.title: Investors Bet on a Faster Fed - MoneyBeat - WSJ

author: Ben Eisen
title: Investors Bet on a Faster Fed - MoneyBeat - WSJ
text: Investors are starting to think the Federal Reserve will lift rates faster than indicated. Those betting on the path of interest rates in the Fed funds futures market see a 45% chance of at least four increases this year, according to CME Group.
